    {
      "id": "PopularPost243008",
      "post_content": "This card has many, many uses. One is to run with discard. Get your opponent down to zero cards in hand, then drop this bad boy. You get to lose cards in hand, whereas your opponent has to sacrifice permanents. After a couple rounds of this, simply sacrifice Descent to itself, and look at the board state.  \n  \nIf you had merely 2 more cards in hand than your opponent ([Mind Rot](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Rot) + [Mind Rot](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Rot)), you have a three-permanent advantage. Which is worse, losing cards in hand, or permanents? Well they 2 more permanents than you for the cost of only your cards in hand, in addition to the fact you can sacrifice it to itself gives you an advantage of 3.  \n  \nAlternatively, run with card draw, token making, etc. for similar effects.",
      "posted_by": "http404error",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost243008\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">This card has many, many uses. One is to run with discard. Get your opponent down to zero cards in hand, then drop this bad boy. You get to lose cards in hand, whereas your opponent has to sacrifice permanents. After a couple rounds of this, simply sacrifice Descent to itself, and look at the board state.<br/><br/>If you had merely 2 more cards in hand than your opponent (<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mind Rot\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Rot\">Mind Rot</a> + <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mind Rot\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Rot\">Mind Rot</a>),  you have a three-permanent advantage. Which is worse, losing cards in hand, or permanents? Well they 2 more permanents than you for the cost of only your cards in hand, in addition to the fact you can sacrifice it to itself gives you an advantage of 3.<br/><br/>Alternatively, run with card draw, token making, etc. for similar effects.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '243008'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy54902\">http404error</span>\r\n                                (5/3/2012 7:52:23 AM)\r\n                            </di